    window.geofeed = function geofeed(options) {
        if (options === undefined || options === null || options.continent === undefined || options.continent === null) return;
        const continent = options.continent.toString();
        if (continent === 'EU') {
            window.PGM.blockScripts = true;
        } else {
            window.PGM.blockScripts = false;
        }
    }

<script type='text/javascript'>
var googletag = googletag || {};
googletag.cmd = googletag.cmd || [];

var PGM = PGM || {};
PGM.ads = PGM.ads || {};
PGM.ads.data = null;

PGM.brightcove = {"account_id":1125911414,"default_player":"SJeOLIT3Hf","amp_player":"iw2jzThx","autoplayers":["HynaCuMbg","S1endnWG9x","HyHqRqMw","SJeOLIT3Hf"]};

window.CLARITY = window.CLARITY || [];

CLARITY.push({
    use: ["ads", "jquery"],
    run: function(Ads, $){

        if( typeof Krux !== 'undefined' ) {
            Ads.addKeyVal("all", "ksg", Krux.segments);
            Ads.addKeyVal("all", "kuid", Krux.user);
        }

        var $embeddedVideos = $('.embedded-content[data-template="video"]');
        if($embeddedVideos.length) {
            // Wish we could do this in the module but it's too late by then
            // for now all embedded videos are autoplay
            Ads.addKeyVal("all", "video", "autoplay");
        } else {
            // Else check if it's one of our autoplay videos
            $('video').each(function () {
                var $vid = $(this),
                    player = $vid.data('player'),
                    account = $vid.data('account');

                if (PGM.brightcove.autoplayers.indexOf(player) >= 0) {
                    // If there are any auto-play vids stop
                    Ads.addKeyVal("all", "video", "autoplay");
                    return false;
                } else if (account) {
                    Ads.addKeyVal("all", "video", "click-to-play");
                    // if there are click-to-plays there could still be an auto-play somewhere, continue
                }
            });
        }
    }
});
</script>

<script>
    window.CLARITY = window.CLARITY || [];

<div class="ad_clarity" data-out-of-page="true" style="display: none;"></div>
<script>

    window.top.pageLevelKeys = {};
    window.top.pageAdZoneFragment = {};
    let pair = '';
    let pairParts = '';
    let key = '';
    let value = '';
    let list = '';
    
    list = 'env=prod|ptype=charts|url=031df4f8|keywords=charts,hot-100,2021-07-29|tags_global=charts,hot-100,2021-07-29|domain=www.billboard.com|';
    list = list.trim().slice(0, -1);
    let listParts = list.split('|');
    for (var i = 0; i < listParts.length; i++) {
        pair = listParts[i];
        if(pair != '' && pair.includes('=')) {
            pairParts = pair.split('=');
            key = pairParts[0].trim().toLowerCase();
            value = pairParts[1].trim();
            if (key === "tags" || key === "tags_global" || key === "keywords") {
                window.top.pageLevelKeys['tag'] = value;
            } else if (key === "ptype" || key === "ctype" || key === "pagetype") {
                window.top.pageLevelKeys['pt'] = value;
            } else if (key === "page" || key === 'contentId​') {
                window.top.pageLevelKeys['ci'] = value;
            }  
        }
    }
    
    window.top.pageAdZoneFragment['zone'] = '';

    CLARITY.push({
        use: ['ads', 'cookies', 'header'],
        run: function(Ads, cookies, header) {
            // @TODO can remove try/catch after this release; wrapping it for now in site/Clarity deploys are out of
            // sync.
            try {
                // Since we have the ad unit available, let Clarity know about it so we don't have to keep passing that
                // in.
                header.setAdUnit('8352/billboard/');
            } catch(err) {
            }
            Ads.site_code = "billboard";
            Ads.zone = "";
            var keywords = [];
            var region = cookies.get('PGMCC') ? cookies.get('PGMCC') : '';
            // Keyword injection
            if (typeof(global_keywords) !== "undefined") {
                keywords = global_keywords;
            }
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "env=prod",
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            });
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "ptype=charts",
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            });
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "url=031df4f8",
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            });
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "keywords=charts,hot-100,2021-07-29",
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            });
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "tags_global=charts,hot-100,2021-07-29",
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            });
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "domain=www.billboard.com",
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            });
                        keywords.push({
                keywords: "",
                keyvalues: "region=" + region,
                paths: "",
                positions: "all"
            })
            Ads.keywords = keywords;
                                }
    });

        
</script>
<script type="text/javascript" async="async" data-cfasync="false" src="https://ads.blogherads.com/static/blogherads.js"></script>
<script type='text/javascript'>
    let detectDevice = function() {
        let device;
        var mobile = /(?:phone|windows\s+phone|ipod|blackberry|(?:android|bb\d+|meego|silk|googlebot) .+?mobile|palm|windows\s+ce|opera mini|avantgo|docomo)/i;
        var tablet = /(?:ipad|playbook|(?:android|bb\d+|meego|silk)(?! .+? mobile))/i;
        if(mobile.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
            device = "mobile";
        } else if(tablet.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
            device = "tablet";
        } else {
            device = "desktop";
        }
        return device;
    };       
    let overideAdZoneIfApplicable = function(adZone) {
        let curPathName = window.location.pathname;
        const constants = {
            chartPageAdUnits: {
                hot100: 'charts/hot-100',
                billboard200: 'charts/billboard-200',
                rbhiphopsongs: 'charts/r-b-hip-hop-albums',
                hot100songs: 'charts/year-end/Hot-100'
            }
        };
        if( curPathName == '/charts/hot-100' ||
            curPathName == '/charts/billboard-200' ||
            curPathName == '/charts/r-b-hip-hop-songs' ||
            curPathName == '/charts/year-end/2018/hot-100-songs' ) {
            const splitPathName = curPathName.split('/');
            let chartLastPath = splitPathName[splitPathName.length-1];
            chartLastPath = chartLastPath.split('-');
            chartLastPath = chartLastPath.join('');
            adZone = constants.chartPageAdUnits[chartLastPath];
        }
        return adZone;
    };             
    var AdSlots = {};
    var blogherads = blogherads || {};
    blogherads.adq = blogherads.adq || [];
    if (window.top.pageLevelKeys !== null) {
        blogherads.adq.push(function() {
            for (const key in window.top.pageLevelKeys) {
                blogherads.setTargeting(key, window.top.pageLevelKeys[key]);
            }
        });
    }
    if (window.top.pageAdZoneFragment !== undefined && window.top.pageAdZoneFragment['zone'] !== null) {
        if (window.top.pageAdZoneFragment['zone'] === '' && window.top.pageLevelKeys !== undefined && window.top.pageLevelKeys['pt'] !== null && window.top.pageLevelKeys['pt'] !== '') {
            window.top.pageAdZoneFragment['zone'] = window.top.pageLevelKeys['pt'];
        }        
        blogherads.adq.push(function() {
            let siteHostname = document.location.hostname;
            if (siteHostname.includes("billboard") || siteHostname.includes("hollywoodreporter")) {
                blogherads.setConf('vertical', `${overideAdZoneIfApplicable(window.top.pageAdZoneFragment['zone'])}`);
            } else if (siteHostname.includes("vibe")) {
                blogherads.setConf('vertical', `${detectDevice()}/${overideAdZoneIfApplicable(window.top.pageAdZoneFragment['zone'])}`);
            }
        });
    }

    var idMap = new Map();
    var pageAdsObserver = new MutationObserver(function(mutations) {

        var adElements = document.querySelectorAll('[data-dark-matter-is-processed="false"]');
        if (adElements.length != 0) {
            blogherads.adq.push(function() {
                for (let i = 0; i < adElements.length; i++) {

                    if (adElements[i].getAttribute("data-dark-matter-is-processed") !== "true") {
                        let adElementType = adElements[i].getAttribute("data-position");
                        adElementType = adElementType.trim().toLowerCase();
                        if (!idMap.has(adElementType)) {
                            idMap.set(adElementType, 1);
                        } else {
                            idMap.set(adElementType, idMap.get(adElementType) + 1);
                        }            
                        let adElementAttribute = document.createAttribute("id");
                        adElementAttribute.value = adElementType + "_" + idMap.get(adElementType);
                        adElements[i].setAttributeNode(adElementAttribute);  
                        if (adElementType === 'footerboard_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[728, 0], 'banner'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).addSize('banner', [970, 90]).setTargeting('pos', 'footerboard_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'leaderboard_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 0], 'flexbanner'],
                                [[728, 0], 'banner'],
                                [[320, 0], 'tinybanner'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).addSize('tinybanner', [[320, 170], [320, 100]]).setTargeting('pos', 'leaderboard_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'rightrail_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 0], 'flexrec'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'rightrail_ad').display();				
                        } else if (adElementType === 'leftrail_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 600], 'flexrec'],
                                [[728, 250], 'medrec'],
                                [[320, 50], 'mobileincontent'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'leftrail_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'contentwell_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[320, 0], 'medrec'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'contentwell_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'parallax_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 0], 'none'],
                                [[320, 0], '300x600'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'parallax_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'native_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 250], 'flexbanner']
                                [[728, 90], 'banner'],
                                [[320, 480], 'tinybanner'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'native_ad')
                            .addSize('tinybanner', [[2, 2], [4, 4], [320, 480]])
                            .addSize('banner', [[2, 2], [4, 4]])
                            .addSize('flexbanner', [[2, 2], [4, 4]]).display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'adhesion') {
                            blogherads.defineSlot('bottom', 'skm-ad-bottom').setTargeting('pos', 'adhesion').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'promo') {
                            blogherads.defineCustomSlot(adElementAttribute.value, [[2, 2], [3, 3]]).setTargeting('pos', 'promo').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'zergnet') {
                            blogherads.defineCustomSlot(adElementAttribute.value, [4, 4]).setTargeting('pos', 'zergnet').setSubAdUnitPath('zergnet').setDefaultAutoRefreshTime(0).display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'out_of_page') {
                            blogherads.defineSlot('inlineoop', adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'out_of_page').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'richmedia_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineCustomSlot(adElementAttribute.value, [1, 1]).setTargeting('pos', 'richmedia_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'autoinject_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[728, 0], 'none'],
                                [[320, 0], 'mobileincontent'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'autoinject_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'middleboard_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 0], 'flexbanner'],
                                [[728, 0], 'banner'],
                                [[320, 0], 'mobileincontent'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'middleboard_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'fluidrail_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 600], 'flexrec'],
                                [[320, 50], 'medrec'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'fluidrail_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'interchart_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 0], 'flexbanner'],
                                [[728, 0], 'banner'],
                                [[320, 0], 'medrec'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'interchart_ad').addSize('banner', [300, 250]).display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'sponsor') {
                            blogherads.defineCustomSlot(adElementAttribute.value, [2, 3]).setTargeting('pos', 'sponsor').setDefaultAutoRefreshTime(0).display();
                        } else if (adElementType === '728x90_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[728, 0], 'banner'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', '728x90_ad').display();
                        } else if (adElementType === 'chartrail_ad') {
                            blogherads.defineResponsiveSlot([
                                [[1024, 0], 'flexrec'],
                                [[728, 0], 'banner'],
                                [[320, 0], 'medrec'],
                                [[0, 0], 'none']
                            ], adElementAttribute.value).setTargeting('pos', 'chartrail_ad').addSize('banner', [300, 250]).display();
                        }
                        adElements[i].setAttribute("data-dark-matter-is-processed", "true");
                    }
                }
            });
        }
    });

    pageAdsObserver.observe(document, {attributes: false, childList: true, characterData: false, subtree:true});

</script>

<script>

    function loadEUScript(source, attributes = {}) {

        const script = document.createElement('script');
        script.type = 'text/javascript';
        script.async = true;
        script.src = source;

        if (typeof attributes === 'object') {
            Object.keys(attributes).forEach(key => {
                script[key] = attributes[key];
                // check for data attribute.
                if (key.startsWith('data')) {
                    script.setAttribute(key, attributes[key]);
                }
            });
        } else if (typeof attributes === 'function') {
            attributes(script);
        }

        document.getElementsByTagName('head')[0].appendChild(script);
    }

    window.geofeed = function geofeed(options) {

        if (options === undefined || options === null || options.state === undefined || options.continent === undefined || options.state === null || options.continent === null) return;

        const state = options.state.toString();
        const continent = options.continent.toString();
        const cprLink = document.getElementById("california_privacy_rights_link");
        const cprLinkBlock = document.getElementById("california_privacy_rights_link_block");
        const dnsmpiLink = document.getElementById("do_not_sell_my_personal_information_link");
        const dnsmpiLinkBlock = document.getElementById("do_not_sell_my_personal_information_link_block");
        const eppLink = document.getElementById("eu_privacy_preferences_link");
        const eppLinkBlock = document.getElementById("eu_privacy_preferences_link_block");

        if (state !== 'CA' && state !== 'NY' && continent !== 'EU') {
            if (cprLinkBlock && cprLink && dnsmpiLinkBlock && dnsmpiLink && eppLinkBlock && eppLink) {
                cprLink.style.display = 'none'
                cprLinkBlock.style.display = 'none';
                dnsmpiLink.style.display = 'none';
                dnsmpiLinkBlock.style.display = 'none';
                eppLink.style.display = 'none';
                eppLinkBlock.style.display = 'none';
            }
        } else if (state === 'CA' || state === 'NY') {
            if (cprLinkBlock && cprLink && dnsmpiLinkBlock && dnsmpiLink && eppLinkBlock && eppLink) {
                cprLink.style.display = 'inline'
                cprLinkBlock.style.display = 'inline';
                dnsmpiLink.style.display = 'inline';
                dnsmpiLinkBlock.style.display = 'inline';
                eppLink.style.display = 'none';
                eppLinkBlock.style.display = 'none';

                dnsmpiLink.addEventListener("click", function (e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay();
                });                
            }
        } else if (continent === 'EU') {
            if (cprLinkBlock && cprLink && dnsmpiLinkBlock && dnsmpiLink && eppLinkBlock && eppLink) {
                cprLink.style.display = 'none'
                cprLinkBlock.style.display = 'none';
                dnsmpiLink.style.display = 'none';
                dnsmpiLinkBlock.style.display = 'none';
                eppLink.style.display = 'inline';
                eppLinkBlock.style.display = 'inline';
                loadEUScript("https://cdn.cookielaw.org/consent/tcf.stub.js", {
                    charset: "UTF-8",
                });
                eppLink.addEventListener("click", function (e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    OneTrust.ToggleInfoDisplay();
                });
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<script>
    window.geofeed = function(options) {
        // string two digit continent code EU, NA, OC, AS, SA, AF
        var continent = options.continent.toString();
        // string two digit ISO country code
        var country = options.country.toString();
        // string two digit state code
        var state = options.state.toString();

        if (state == 'CA') {
            document.getElementById("ot-sdk-btn").style.visibility = "visible";
        } else {
            document.getElementById("ot-sdk-btn").style.visibility = "hidden";
        }
        // similar logic can be included for country level and state level users.
    }
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    const arrayStringInUrl = ( stringsArray ) => {
        return stringsArray.some(function(string) { return window.location.href.indexOf(string) >= 0 })
    }
    window.pianoDebugOutput = ( message ) => {
        const environments = [ 'local.', 'dev.' , 'staging.', 'int.' ];
        if( arrayStringInUrl( ['/articles/','/close-calls/'] ) && arrayStringInUrl( environments ) ){
            console.log( `%c${message}`, "background: #800080; color: #fff; padding: 3px" );
        }
    }
    window.PGM.createScript("//api.tinypass.com/xbuilder/experience/load?aid=Ow9jtiXxtz", function () {
        tp = window.tp || [];
        var previousPage = 'https://www.billboard.com/';
        var url = document.referrer;
        if ( url !== '' && (url.indexOf(location.protocol + '//' + location.host) === 0) ) {
            previousPage = url;
        }
        // enable GA events
        tp.push(["init", function () {
            tp.push(["setDebug",  ]);
             // ... integration code here
             tp.enableGACrossDomainLinking();
         }]);
        // Debug if article has Pay Wall
        tp.push(["addHandler", "experienceExecute", function(event) {

            let pageExperiences = event.result.experiences;
            // Output experiences
            let pageExperiencesOutput = '';
            pageExperiences.map( ( experience, index ) => {
                pageExperiencesOutput = pageExperiencesOutput + `\n${index+1}. ${experience.title}`;
            });
            if (typeof window.pianoDebugOutput === "function") {
                window.pianoDebugOutput(`Piano Page Experiences: ${pageExperiencesOutput}`);
            }
            let title = 'Infinite Scroll Article Overlay';
            let hasValue = function (obj, key, value) {
                return obj.hasOwnProperty(key) && obj[key] === value;
            }
            const PianoResponseMessage = 'Piano Composer Response Infinite scroll Layout -';
            let jsConsoleMessage = '';
            if (pageExperiences.some(function (pageExperiences) {
                return hasValue(pageExperiences, "title", title);
            })) {
                jsConsoleMessage = PianoResponseMessage + ' Pay walled';
            } else {
                jsConsoleMessage = PianoResponseMessage + ' No Pay wall';
            }
            // Output paywall result
            if (typeof window.pianoDebugOutput === "function") {
                window.pianoDebugOutput(jsConsoleMessage);
            }
        } ]);
        tp.push(["setCustomVariable", "parentUrl", window.location.href]);
        tp.push(["setCustomVariable", "previousPage", previousPage]);
        //Set closecall status variable
        if(arrayStringInUrl(['/close-calls/'])){
            let closeCallTimeStamp = 0;
            let eventStartPassed = false;
            let closeCallState = 'pre-event';
            if(!isNaN()){
                let current_timestamp = + new Date();
                eventStartPassed = closeCallTimeStamp < current_timestamp;
                closeCallState = `${eventStartPassed ? 'post' : 'pre'}-event`;
            }
            tp.push(["setCustomVariable", "closeCallTimestamp", closeCallTimeStamp]);
            tp.push(["setCustomVariable", "closeCallState", closeCallState]);
            window.pianoDebugOutput("Close Call "+ (eventStartPassed ?  "Paywalled - Post Event"  : " No Paywall - Pre Event" ) +"\nClose Call State  | Close Call timestamp " + closeCallTimeStamp + " | " + new Date(closeCallTimeStamp).toLocaleDateString(navigator.language, {hour: '2-digit', minute:'2-digit'})) ;
        };
        tp.push(['setUsePianoIdUserProvider', true]);
        tp.push(["setContentSection",  "chart_landing"  ]);
        //abandon cart cookie logic start
        //_abandon_user = {anon, free}
        //_abandon_item = {termId}
        tp.push(["addHandler", "startCheckout", function(event) {
            if (event.userToken === '') {
                document.cookie = "_abandon_user=anon";
            } else {
                document.cookie = "_abandon_user=free";
            }
            document.cookie = "_abandon_item=" + event.termId;
        }]);
        tp.push(["addHandler", "loginSuccess", function(event) {
            if (event.source === 'OFFER') {
                document.cookie = "_abandon_user=free";
            }
        }]);
        tp.push(["addHandler", "checkoutComplete", function(event) {
            document.cookie = "_abandon_user=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;";
            document.cookie = "_abandon_item=;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;";
        }]);
        // content tracking data
            if (typeof window.tp !== 'undefined'){
    tp.push(["setContentCreated", ""]);
    tp.push(["setContentAuthor", [
     ]]);

            if (typeof window.pianoDebugOutput === "function") {
            window.pianoDebugOutput( "Article:\nThe Hot 100\nPiano Tags Sent:\nWeekly" );
        }
        tp.push(["setTags", ["Weekly"]]);
        }
    });
</script>
